       AWS  IoT-Data  enables secure, bi-directional communication between In-
       ternet-connected things (such as sensors, actuators, embedded  devices,
       or  smart appliances) and the AWS cloud. It implements a broker for ap-
       plications and things to publish messages over HTTP (Publish)  and  re-
       trieve,  update, and delete shadows. A shadow is a persistent represen-
       tation of your things and their state in the AWS cloud.

       Find the endpoint address for actions in the AWS IoT data plane by run-
       ning this CLI command:
